{"tid":2383402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慘！騎共享單車坐墊脫落　男子後庭被金屬管架刺穿","createTime":"2021-01-28T01:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:51:36.000Z","uid":271829,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf2cda6f418618e08d46ee873249a6662d87951","tid":2383402,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/5iPygBzSK6wYJDLW-zUwJ7vtgLw=/996x560/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NWU37MLBUJC3HLZH45KLBBVHEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5iPygBzSK6wYJDLW-zUwJ7vtgLw%3D%2F996x560%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNWU37MLBUJC3HLZH45KLBBVHEI.jpg&h=7e600b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國廣州男子其共享單車時坐墊脫落，下方鋼管直接刺入他的後停，動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n實在是太悽慘了！中國廣東一名男子，日前在騎「共享單車」時，單車的坐墊意外脫落，坐墊下的金屬管直接刺穿他的臀部，男子連同單車一起倒在路邊無法動彈。<br />\n<br />\n《中新網》報導，這起意外發生在中國廣東省廣州，周二(26日)晚間10時許，一名男子在一處公車站旁租用了共享單車，才剛騎上沒多遠，疑因與其他車輛發生小碰撞，單車的坐墊竟然掉落，男子並未注意用力坐下，坐墊下方的金屬管便直接刺入他的臀部，人車同時倒地動彈不得。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210128/OV2NODSL65HMNE3SWVQFETPLPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210128%2FOV2NODSL65HMNE3SWVQFETPLPE%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=4f9f135e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210128%2FOV2NODSL65HMNE3SWVQFETPLPE%2F&h=bcecec6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210128/OV2NODSL65HMNE3SWVQFETPLPE/</a>"},{"pid":"713b2322186c96c2d0056cdfeafca6e2d34b9d37","tid":2383402,"uid":56999,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:24:25.000Z","msg":"跟住條友會向單車公司索償<br />\n<br />\n跟住每日幾百日插屎眼要求賠錢"},{"pid":"d772213646b28fef32f9b6a51e1816deb2307b40","tid":2383402,"uid":65473,"lik